Scan all values in file.

Useful for performance testing

Parameters
[in]columnsthe column numbers to scan. If empty scans all
[in]column_batch_sizenumber of values to read at a time when scanning column
[in]readera ParquetFileReader instance
Returns
number of semantic rows in file
